\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In the MCMC, we sample 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{t}$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $t=1,2,...,100$
\end_inset

 to estimate the temporal evolution of biomass over the time period of interest.
 
\end_layout

